readme:
# Atom Anmol Syntax
---

A syntax theme for [Atom Material UI](https://github.com/silvestreh/atom-material-ui). Inspired by Anmol Jagetia's [SublimeText theme](https://github.com/anmoljagetia/dotfiles/blob/master/sublime/anmol.tmTheme).
